<div class="section-description">
	                            <div class="attribute-short">
                    
<p>Hacker News Delta is an open website product project by 7x.</p><p>For any issue you might have, feel free to <a href="/about/contact" target="_self">contact the HNDelta Crew</a> directly.</p>                </div>
                    
